Motormaster tried hard to right himself, squirming up against the wall.
"Ohhhh. thanks Astro" he boomed. He was extreemly weak and was very
unsucssesful at uprighting himself. "We'll go back to earth, and while I am
repairing, you can deal with the Predacons. We'll plan another assault for
another time" with that he laid back down, coughed up a bit of oil, and
pulled out the energon cube. "Lukily this didnt detonate. Endbringer,
Killfest, could one of you refule Astroblast" he said weakly holding up the
cube.
